<p>Which theorem(s) is/are correct about the regression equation Y = b<sub>0</sub> + b<sub>1</sub>X?</p>
<p>I. Y actually represents the predicted value by the regression.<br />
II. b<sub>0 </sub>is the mean value of Y when X equals 0</p>
</p>]]></text>
