<generalfeedback format="html">
<text><![CDATA[<p>
<p>Theorem I is correct because the regression equation predicts values of Y predicted by means of the regression line a + b<sub>1</sub>X.<br />
Theorem II is also correct because if you replace X with 0 then the equation Y=b<sub>0</sub>. This means that the pre-measured value of Y (or alternatively, the average Y) is equal to the constant.</p>
</p>]]></text>
</generalfeedback>
